 />\n可在耀才網站找到<br />\n各位千其唔好做犯法嘢"},{"pid":"9760ec4979cdd317335bbe2e5bc1d909f0904546","tid":1872034,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe30146cccb53e19ecc5d7715a2888c4a32b50b","tid":1872034,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af16ad5cd577fbb7d1354fbd3712a909bb4814d","tid":1872034,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"集火埋新聞部班賤種, 連坐埋仲好"},{"pid":"19127336edbc38a8f0b87872352410f29f715f4a","tid":1872034,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af16ad5cd577fbb7d1354fbd3712a909bb4814d","tid":1872034,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"集火埋新聞部班賤種, 連坐埋仲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"其實d 主播都係照稿讀, <br />\n但係集火唔到寫稿果個"},{"pid":"20f5323a689dad5a08aa0ab341d917d2a38c22f7","tid":1872034,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19127336edbc38a8f0b87872352410f29f715f4a","tid":1872034,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af16ad5cd577fbb7d1354fbd3712a909bb4814d","tid":1872034,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"集火埋新聞部班賤種, 連坐埋仲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"其實d 主播都係照稿讀, <br />\n但係集火唔到寫稿果個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"警察都係跟order做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc3385660bd73ea8f1f763172bb7699432ae1f5","tid":1872034,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f5323a689dad5a08aa0ab341d